# Mobile

- 44px min touch: `min-h-[44px] min-w-[44px]`; clear at `sm:min-h-0 sm:min-w-0`.
- `touch-manipulation` on controls.
- Spacing: `px-3 sm:px-4 lg:px-6`; inputs `text-base sm:text-sm`.
- Dialog: `max-w-[calc(100%-1rem)]` mobile; tables `overflow-x-auto`.
